snippet.title: Longplay of Hydro Thunder
snippet.description:
Longplay of Hydro Thunder, played with the NTSC version on the Sega Dreamcast. This game's version was released on Sep. 9th, 1999. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

By: Spazbo4
